text: Èrica Gonçalves Do Canto (born 9 May 2002) is an Andorran footballer who plays as a defender for Andorran-based Spanish Women's First Division of Catalonia club ENFAF and the Andorra women's national team. ==International career== Gonçalves capped for Andorra at senior level in a 0–2 friendly loss to Luxembourg on 10 November 2018. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Andorran women's footballers Category:Andorra women's international footballers Category:Andorran people of Portuguese descent
